      • calculateWorkdays

        public int calculateWorkdays(double start,
                             double end,
                             double[] holidays)
        Calculate how many workdays are there between a start and an end date, as excel representations, considering a range of holidays.(考虑一系列假期，以Excel形式计算开始日期和结束日期之间有多少个工作日。)
        Parameters:
        start - start date.(开始-开始日期。)
        end - end date.(结束-结束日期。)
        holidays - an array of holidays.(假期-一系列假期。)
        Returns:
        number of workdays between start and end dates, including both dates.(开始日期和结束日期（包括这两个日期）之间的工作天数。)

      • calculateWorkdays

        public java.util.Date calculateWorkdays(double start,
                                        int workdays,
                                        double[] holidays)
        Calculate the workday past x workdays from a starting date, considering a range of holidays.(考虑一系列假期，计算从开始日期起过去x个工作日的工作日。)
        Parameters:
        start - start date.(开始-开始日期。)
        workdays - number of workdays to be past from starting date.(工作日-从开始日期起要过去的工作日数。)
        holidays - an array of holidays.(假期-一系列假期。)
        Returns:
        date past x workdays.(过去x个工作日的日期。)

      • pastDaysOfWeek

        protected int pastDaysOfWeek(double start,
                             double end,
                             int dayOfWeek)
        Calculates how many days of week past between a start and an end date.(计算开始日期和结束日期之间的一周过去了多少天。)
        Parameters:
        start - start date.(开始-开始日期。)
        end - end date.(结束-结束日期。)
        dayOfWeek - a day of week as represented by Calendar constants.(dayOfWeek -由日历常数表示的一周中的一天。)
        Returns:
        how many days of week past in this interval.(在这段时间里，一周过去了多少天。)

      • calculateNonWeekendHolidays

        protected int calculateNonWeekendHolidays(double start,
                                          double end,
                                          double[] holidays)
        Calculates how many holidays in a list are workdays, considering an interval of dates.(考虑日期间隔，计算列表中有多少个假期是工作日。)
        Parameters:
        start - start date.(开始-开始日期。)
        end - end date.(结束-结束日期。)
        holidays - an array of holidays.(假期-一系列假期。)
        Returns:
        number of holidays that occur in workdays, between start and end dates.(工作日中开始和结束日期之间的假期数。)
